Package: cooloRsampler
Type: Package
Title: Returns a Randomly Generated Color Palette From Coolors (https://coolors.co/)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kristen Akey
Maintainer: The package maintainer <kkakey999@gmail.com>
Description: This package features the `coolor_sampler()` function, which 
    grabs a randomly generated color palette of 2 to 9 colors from Coolors (https://coolors.co/). 
    Users specify the number of colors they would like in their palette, and the 
    functions returns the HEX codes of the randomly generated palette.
